IBM Rational Software Architect Designer Description

IBM Rational Software Architect Designer will improve your solution delivery results. The solution reduces complexity and helps you understand, collaborate, and communicate better. It helps you to manage risk and compliance easier while increasing productivity and quality of services and applications. Graphical abstractions make it easier to deliver your innovation and maintenance backlogs quicker. To improve your delivery outcomes, ensure that your entire team understands and contributes to your project. Abstraction can be used to preserve design intentions and tribal memories, and to provide auditable evidence that policies have been followed. This integrated design and development platform simplifies architectural modeling.
